8\u00d7 \u2014 partly cash-backed.","\u2212 Leveraged (D/E 0.60\u00d7, interest cover 1.3\u00d7).","+ Profit up 32% YoY (latest TTM) and accelerating."],"rule":"Points across the four business flags: +1 for each that is 'good' (quality, cash conversion, balance-sheet safety, earnings momentum), \u22121 for each that is 'weak'. Verdict: positive at +2 or more, negative at \u22122 or less."},"Valuation":{"verdict":"neutral","score":0,"drivers":["\u00b7 P/E at the 42-percentile of its 10-yr range \u2014 mid-range vs its own history."],"rule":"Cheap \u2014 P/E below the 30th percentile of its own 10-year range \u2014 scores +2 (supportive); expensive (above the 70th) scores \u22122; mid-range is 0. A peak/cyclical-earnings flag discounts a cheap read to +1. NOTE: 'positive' means the multiple looks supportive vs the stock's OWN history \u2014 it is NOT a buy call."},"Ownership":{"verdict":"neutral","score":0,"drivers":[],"rule":"Points: +1 promoter stake rising \u00b7 \u22121 promoter stake falling more than 1pp in a year \u00b7 \u22121 promoter pledge above 10% \u00b7 +1 for each of FII / DII accumulating (>0.5pp in a year). Verdict: positive at +1 or more, negative at \u22121 or less."}},"top_positives":["Trades above its 200-day average (+206%).","50-day average above the 200-day (golden cross).","Within 0% of its 52-week high.","Profit up 32% YoY (latest TTM) and accelerating."],"key_risks":["Lagging the NIFTY 500 by -3090pp over 12 months.","Leveraged (D/E 0.60\u00d7, interest cover 1.3\u00d7)."],"monitor_next":["Next quarterly results (board-meeting date is an MVP-2 placeholder).","Re-rating toward / away from its median P/E (44.4\u00d7).","Relative-strength inflection vs its sector index.","Promoter pledge / institutional-holding changes next quarter."],"caveats":["Thinly traded \u2014 median ~\u20b90.68 cr/day (< \u20b91 cr); signals/exits may slip.","corporate-action gaps, illiquid names, or a short listing history can distort returns/DMA/RS."],"confidence":"medium","disclaimer":"Diagnostics only \u2014 a structured reading of price behaviour, business fundamentals, valuation and ownership for your OWN judgement. This is NOT a buy/sell/hold recommendation.","method":"Each dimension is a transparent points tally of the named signals listed beneath it \u2014 open a dimension to see the exact signals that fired and its rule. Verdict = positive at +2 or more / negative at \u22122 or less for Market, Business and Valuation; \u00b11 for Ownership. A 'positive' valuation means the multiple looks supportive vs the stock's OWN history \u2014 never a buy call."},"data_quality":{"price_asof":"2026-06-25","fundamentals_fetched":"2026-06-20","has_fundamentals":true,"has_shareholding":true,"liquidity_warning":"Thinly traded \u2014 median ~\u20b90.68 cr/day (< \u20b91 cr); signals/exits may slip.","note":"Market data is daily and current; fundamentals & shareholding are as of the last cached Screener fetch (quarterly/annual). Confidence is lower for thin or short-history names."}}